<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idc9d00fde-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idc9d00fdf-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/102/575/s1617">section 1617 of Pub. L. 102–575</ref> was renumbered section 1633 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t43/s390h–15">section 390h–15 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
